been selected as the projected host for the regional tournament next weekend. 
If all goes according to form, No. 10 USC will travel to second-ranked Stanford 
for the West Regional, and seventh-ranked Long Beach will play host to the 
Northwest Regional. WENDY WITHERSPOON 
