<P>
HIGH SCHOOL FOOTBALL / CITY SECTION SEMIFINALS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By MICHAEL LAZARUS 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Birmingham 27, Wilson 20 -- Courtney Blunt gained 221 yards in 25 carries and 
scored three touchdowns for Birmingham (7-5-1) in a 3-A semifinal at Wilson 
(10-3). 
</P>
<P>
 Blunt had to do most of his work without his fullback, Marvin Powell, who 
suffered a neck injury in the second quarter and was taken to County USC 
Medical Center as a precaution. MICHAEL LAZARUS 
</P>
