<P>
HIGH SCHOOL FOOTBALL / SOUTHERN SECTION SEMIFINALS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By GEORGE ALFANO 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Moreno Valley Canyon Springs 28, Riverside North 13 -- Ryan Roques scored four 
touchdowns -- two on offense, one on defense and one on a kick return -- to 
lead Canyon Springs (12-1) in a Division IV semifinal at UC Riverside. 
</P>
<P>
 Roques, a senior, ran 95 yards with an interception for a first-quarter 
touchdown and Canyon Springs never looked back. GEORGE ALFANO 
</P>
