HIGH SCHOOL FOOTBALL / SOUTHERN SECTION SEMIFINALS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By BRIAN BULLOCK 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Newport Harbor 13, Santa Ana Foothill 10 -- Brian Johnson's one-yard touchdown 
run on fourth down in overtime lifted Newport Harbor (13-0) to a Division V 
victory at Tustin High. 
</P>
<P>
 Arroyo Grande 34, Ganesha 6 -- Andy Sowell scored three touchdowns for the 
Eagles (11-1) in a Division VII semifinal at Arroyo Grande. 
</P>
<P>
 Sowell scored on runs of one and three yards and a 42-yard interception. BRIAN 
BULLOCK 
</P>
