<HEADLINE>
<P>
A LITTLE BIT OF HISTORY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 More than nine years and 97 matches after it began, Pierce College's winning 
streak in Metropolitan Conference tennis matches ended in 1985 with a 5-1 loss 
to Harbor. 
</P>
<P>
 The Brahmas won their first Ojai tournament title that year, which was a treat 
for Coach Paul Xanthos, who played in the tournament as a Los Angeles City 
College freshman in 1939. 
</P>
