Hall, 1 Civic Center Plaza. 
</P>
<P>
 Hours: City Hall is open Monday through Thursday, 7:30 a.m.-5:30 p.m., and 
alternate Fridays, 8 a.m.-5 p.m. Permit counter is open Monday through 
Thursday, 7:30 a.m.-5:30 p.m., and alternate Fridays, 8 a.m.-5 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 Telephone: (714) 724-6000 
</P>
