O.C. RELIGION NOTES / DAYE CLARK: CHURCH TO MARK 75TH ANNIVERSARY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By DAYE CLARK 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Community Presbyterian Church in San Juan Capistrano will celebrate its 75th 
anniversary on Sunday. The Rev. Robert Schwenck will lead services at 9 and 
10:45 a.m., and ministers who served the church in the past will participate. 
</P>
<P>
 A church history exhibit will be on display, and refreshments will be 
available in the hospitality room from 8:30 a.m. to 12:30 p.m. The church is at 
32202 Del Obispo St. Information: (714) 493-1502. 
</P>
