vs. La Verne Lutheran; 27 vs. Riverside Sherman Indian; 31 at La Sierra 
Academy. 
</P>
<P>
 February 2 vs. CSDR; 7 vs. Anza Hamilton; 10 at La Verne Lutheran. 
