<P>
 RECORD AT SCHOOL: 3-19 04,20,05,06,04 RETURNING STARTERS YR. HGT. P LaCoya 
Cole So. 5-6 G Ann-Marie Harbour So. 5-3 G Melissa McDaniel So. 5-8 F Jennifer 
