 Academy 05,19,08,09,19,19 *2*League *2*Overall School W L W L St. Margaret's 8 
0 16 2 Liberty Christian 6 2 14 9 Cal Lutheran 3 5 9 7 Connelly 3 5 4 13 S.E. 
