</P>
<P>
 RECORD AT SCHOOL: 81 - 82 04,20,05,06,04 RETURNING STARTERS YR. HGT. P Lisa 
Bradberry Sr. 6-0 F Karen Crary Sr. 5-6 G 04,15,05,06,04 TOP RETURNERS YR. HGT. 
