Olivier Jr. 6-1 C Danielle Pierce Jr. 6-0 C OUTLOOK 
</P>
<P>
 The Eagles move to the Academy League this season, which is unfortunate for 
the rest of the league. Although seven seniors graduated from last year's team, 
Shelton feels he has great athletes in the wings and should be able to win the 
