<P>
 Boys' basketball -- The preview capsule for Edison in Friday's Times Orange 
County listed the wrong schedule.The Chargers' remaining schedule: 
</P>
<P>
 December 9 at Santa Margarita; 12-17 at Sonora Cage Classic; 19-22 at Tracy 
tournament; 26-30 at Estancia Coast Classic. 
</P>
<P>
 January 3 at Irvine; 6 vs. Edison; 11 at Fountain Valley; 13 vs. Los Alamitos; 
18 at Huntington Beach; 20 vs. Marina; 27 at Esperanza. 
</P>
<P>
 February 1 vs. Fountain Valley; 3 at Los Alamitos; 8 vs. Huntington Beach; 10 
at Marina. 
